snippet.title: Turkey Hunting USA (2001)  Arcade Gameplay
snippet.description:
Turkey Hunting USA was produced by Sammy USA Corporation in 2000.

Sammy USA Corporation released 11 different machines in our database under this trade name, starting in 1994.

Other machines made by Sammy USA Corporation during the time period Turkey Hunting USA was produced include Deer Hunting USA, Pokemon Catch, Extreme Hunting, Wing Shooting Championship, Trophy Hunting, Lee's Stop 'N Win, Sports Arena, and Magic Mr. X.

An interactive shooting game where players go hunting for wild turkeys.
